query:

  dataType,
  lastSyncAt,
  status,
  recordCount,
  errorMessage
FROM twDataSyncStatus

LIMIT 5)

  'US' as market,
  dataType,
  lastSyncAt,
  status,
  recordCount,
  errorMessage

LIMIT 5)
ORDER BY lastSyncAt DESC
